Feature 2: Meeting Scheduling & Dashboard

This feature allows users to create, view, and organize meetings while providing a quick overview of their progress.

Epic 2.1: Meeting Creation

Users need a way to create and manage meetings.

User Stories:

Create Meeting: As a user, I want to create a new meeting with a title and date so that I can schedule upcoming meetings.

View Meetings: As a user, I want to view upcoming and past meetings to easily access meeting information.

Open Meeting Details: As a user, I want to open a meeting page to manage its agenda points and tasks.

Epic 2.2: Meeting Dashboard

Users need a central page to monitor meetings and tasks.

User Stories:

View Dashboard: As a user, I want to see a dashboard listing all meetings so that I can quickly navigate between them.

Track Progress: As a user, I want to see the number of open and closed agenda points for each meeting to monitor team progress.

Quick Navigation: As a user, I want to access meeting details directly from the dashboard to save time.